column5: Maybe, but I guess the video explains it well
Thank you so much for this wonderful lecture
This is still complex explanation, don't you think?

Very happy for you xD  
I have some questions, if you don't mind:  
\- height, weight?  
\- age?  
\- ADHD type?  
\- have you tried Adderall or similar drugs?  
\- what was your experience with strattera? what about sleep?

Wow, Thank you. I always feel I wanna be the helper guy... and this post makes so much sense. Although you'd expect that people (helpers) know these things, when you have good intentions you do not notice the bad/side effects ... and yes you are making promises that you might not keep...

Thank you for this post
